      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles to stay idle and there is a noticeable leak in the transmission system that needs immediate repair. Externally, the car has extensive rust along the rocker panels and a large dent on the rear bumper, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including several tears in the upholstery. This is an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or for use as a parts vehicle.",
