      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a brand-new home. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape, perfect for your daily commutes or weekend getaways! It drives like a dream and has been well-loved. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels for yourself. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
