      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This driver-spec example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential for precise power distribution. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry, offering the communicative handling and balanced damping characteristic of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
