      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman offers a thrilling driving experience for those who value performance over a museum-grade finish. The Agate Grey Metallic paint maintains a brilliant luster, though a careful walk-around reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small curb scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel. Inside, the black leather interior is clean and well-preserved; while there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the cabin remains free of odors and tears. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. I have recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush. The mid-mounted turbocharged engine delivers power smoothly, and the PDK transmission remains responsive and crisp. All interior electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, are fully operational. This is a reliable, well-maintained sports car that is ready for the daily commute or weekend canyon runs.",
